title: Earth Origins Market Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Salad bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A veg-friendly cafe inside the market with seating. Offers labeled vegan food choices including soups, wraps, sandwiches. Has a cold salad selection in the deli area that includes several vegan salads like curried tofu salad, Asian style tempeh, kale salad, vegan pasta salad, and bbq seitan. Staff is knowledgeable about the vegan lifestyle and will show you which prepared foods are vegan. In the location of the now defunct Railway Market.
